function inViewport(el) {
var bounding = el.getBoundingClientRect();

return (
bounding.top < (window.innerHeight || document.documentElement.clientHeight) &&
bounding.left < (window.innerWidth || document.documentElement.clientWidth) &&
bounding.bottom > 0 &&
bounding.right > 0
);
